Package: oxydraw
Version: @VERSION@
Section: web
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6, ca-certificates
Maintainer: Rodrigo Valeri <rsvalerio@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/rsvalerio/oxydraw
Description: Self-hosted Excalidraw backend, in Rust
 Self-hosted Excalidraw backend, written in Rust. Serves the original
 Excalidraw web UI from a single binary with embedded SQLite persistence:
 anonymous shareable links, a Socket.IO collaboration relay, and the Firebase
 emulation the unmodified frontend expects.
